 sua forma corporea.\nAttende la venuta di un eroe.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/8/", "name": "it"}}, {"text": "Dispositivo que permite aumentar forzadamente\nlas características de los Pokémon.\nEs un prototipo imperfecto.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/7/", "name": "es"}}, {"text": "Nach dem Zerfall seines Körpers nahm Reshiram\ndiese Form an. Man sagt, es warte auf die Ankunft\neines Helden.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/6/", "name": "de"}}, {"text": "Ce sont les derniers restes du corps de Reshiram.\nOn dit qu’ils attendent l’apparition d’un héros.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/5/", "name": "fr"}}, {"text": "레시라무의 육체가 허물어져\n변화한 모습. 영웅의\n등장을 기다린다고 여겨진다.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/3/", "name": "ko"}}, {"text": "レシラムの　にくたいが　ほろび\nへんかした　すがた。えいゆうの\nとうじょうを　まっていると　される。", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/1/", "name": "ja"}}, {"text": "Reshiram’s body was destroyed and\nchanged into this stone. It is said to\nbe waiting for the emergence of a hero.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/14/", "name": "black-2-white-2"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/9/", "name": "en"}}, {"text": "Reshiram’s body was destroyed and\nchanged into this stone. It is said to\nbe waiting for the emergence of a hero.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/versio